{"tid":1650501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你再放過蛋糕女 場運動先真正完","createTime":"2019-10-13T03:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T19:12:21.000Z","uid":196544,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7381ac0ea46e000274bd0718178c167164fb01d3","tid":1650501,"uid":196544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"你地攬撚住佢同左膠有咩分別呀<br />\n你唔割佢 姐係認同佢做既野？<br />\n當年第一日出火魔法<br />\n又屌曬鬼咁<br />\n佢地唔係手足？<br />\n點解你地同左膠一樣<br />\n係呢D時間要保護D唔係同路人既垃圾<br />\n明顯就行一轉就算既賤人<br />\n比狗打唔係最傷心<br />\n佢地做既野係精神打擊<br />\n你走去攬佢地？<br />\n <br />\n我重申一次<br />\n佢地係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">慶祝兩次生日再加上懷疑呃錢食人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我返到屋企想食宵夜都要諗下夠唔夠錢用<br />\n果班閪人係到做D咁既野都可以原諒？<br />\n係咪今日裝修有人入中銀搶錢你地都攬<br />\n係抗爭既道德標準高到咁<br />\n對住傷害真手足既就降低到咁<br />\n第一次冇道歉 第二次冇誠意<br />\n你為左幾條假手足放棄真手足<br />\n我依家就係發悔氣 唔撚開心呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb8be5ce7cbcc31f920d1df4ef7245f61b92497","tid":1650501,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnAJUrV.jpg&h=222a48c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6dbf8f566b79a3a470db5f3d6117696543c748ff","tid":1650501,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:17:59.000Z","msg":"冷處理"},{"pid":"12f79f0b071ccd9e94fdad0010d298cfb7229b01","tid":1650501,"uid":99705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"唔係攬佢<br />\n而係無聊花生講兩句咪算"},{"pid":"2e4b2697632c8795b3c302a14828c1dd0475ff95","tid":1650501,"uid":273727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ab3jAj0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\